name: The Retch
flavourText: But the grain grew twisted and the water turned dark and those who partook of Mother Gull's gift birthed monsters that fed on the flesh of one another.

name: The Pandemonius
flavourText: A single moment sets in motion an eternal fall, beneath which all are buried.

name: The Covenant
flavourText: My Soul is your Strength My Price is your Blood

name: The Brass Dome
flavourText: The turtle's shell one day becomes its tomb.

name: Mark of the Elder
flavourText: Be not stirred by the Void.

name: Presence of Chayula
flavourText: The dreamer stirs, the world trembles.

name: Mark of the Shaper
flavourText: Let madness take control.

name: The Squire
flavourText: Judge not the weak, for they empower the strong.

name: Kaom's Heart
flavourText: The warrior who fears will fall.

name: Atziri's Step
flavourText: Those who dance are considered insane by those who cannot hear the music.' - Atziri, Queen of the Vaal

name: Solstice Vigil
flavourText: Time, like light, can be refracted into all its myriad colours. The first shade is beautiful, but the last will drive the unwary insane.

name: Berek's Respite
flavourText: With Flame licking at his heels Berek berated the clouds Until vengeful Storm spewed forth his rains And Berek held on tight As Fire screamed and steamed And fled.' - Berek and the Untamed

name: Crystallised Omniscience
flavourText: That winter, scorched refugees emerged from the shrine, speaking only in strange tongues. They prayed to a new symbol of power, not out of love, but out of fear.

name: Ashes of the Stars
flavourText: A single facet contains the wisdom of countless disintegrated worlds.

name: Impossible Escape
flavourText: She was the last of countless progeny bred to test the limits of limitless power. In the cosmic prison of her birth, her siblings fought each other to the death for supremacy. She alone reached her limit... and broke through.

name: Ventor's Gamble
flavourText: In a blaze of glory, An anomaly defying all odds The 'unkillable' beast met the divine And Ventor met his latest trophy.

name: Headhunter
flavourText: A man's soul rules from a cavern of bone, learns and judges through flesh-born windows. The heart is meat. The head is where the Man is.' - Lavianga, Advisor to Kaom

name: Watcher's Eye
flavourText: One by one, they stood their ground against a creature they had no hope of understanding, let alone defeating, and one by one, they became a part of it.

name: Badge of the Brotherhood
flavourText: Greater than any blade, agility and intellect will be your weapons.

name: Brutal Restraint
flavourText: They believed themselves the most ordered, but that tradition turned their forests to salt.

name: Militant Faith
flavourText: They believed themselves the utmost faithful, but that conviction became oppression.

name: Thread of Hope
flavourText: Though we cannot touch; one thought, one wish, through centuries alone in darkness.

name: Split Personality
flavourText: You need not go looking for a second opinion.

name: Unnatural Instinct
flavourText: I don't know how I know, I just know that I know.

name: Lethal Pride
flavourText: They believed themselves the greatest warriors, but that savagery turned upon their own.

name: Mageblood
flavourText: Rivers of power course through your veins.

name: Glorious Vanity
flavourText: They believed themselves the pinnacle of civilisation, but that height toppled their empire.

name: Shavronne's Wrappings
flavourText: Shavronne's apparel became ever more extravagant as her body and soul became ever more corrupted.

name: Starforge
flavourText: The end is written into the beginning.

name: Voidforge
flavourText: A weapon born of nothingness, can only create more nothingness.

name: Megalomaniac
flavourText: If you're going to act like you're better than everyone else, make sure you are.

name: Perseverance
flavourText: Some blows must be evaded. Some blows must be endured. The trick is to tell them apart.' - Daresso, the Sword King

name: Carcass Jack
flavourText: ...The discomfort shown by the others is amusing, but none can deny that my work has made quite the splash...' - Maligaro's Journal

name: Darkray Vectors
flavourText: Sirrius flew on wings of light, faster than wind, faster than thought. But try as he might to outrun the darkness, it was there, at every turn, waiting for him.' - Azmerian legend

name: Rat's Nest
flavourText: A lad with no fear of the pest Let rats fill his helmet in jest When they picked his skull clean Where his head should have been Was naught but a vermin-filled nest!

name: Belly of the Beast
flavourText: There is no safer place Than the Belly of the Beast

name: Inpulsa's Broken Heart
flavourText: Don't hesitate; bring death to all, conclusively and swiftly, or they will give you the same treatment.

name: Abyssus
flavourText: When you have slain all of your enemies, what is left to fear?

name: Hrimsorrow
flavourText: Of ancient giants, none remain, Their only trace is timeless pain.

name: Starkonja's Head
flavourText: There was no hero made out of Starkonja's death, but merely a long sleep made eternal.

name: Devoto's Devotion
flavourText: Swift as thought are the actions of Man when borne on wings of divine providence.

name: Heatshiver
flavourText: Give of your heated passions. Give of your cold resolve. You will be repaid.

name: Hand of Wisdom and Action
flavourText: She thinks and we act. She acts and we think. Fragments of the whole that washes clean the skies.

name: Soul Taker
flavourText: It is too easy for the soul to escape from an open heart.

name: Nebulis
flavourText: The vastness of the cosmos holds energies beyond comprehension, should one have the fortitude to grasp them.

name: Cospri's Malice
flavourText: Breathe deep, my child. Let the frigid air engulf your soul. Embrace the eternal cold, And it will embrace you back.

name: The Taming
flavourText: Moon after moon did Berek make fools Of the great and Untamed Three Until malice for a Brother Slew the hatred of the Other And Berek did hunt Alone and free.' - Berek and the Untamed

name: The Unseen Hue
flavourText: They seek that which lies before them, shining Yours is a special curse, nipping at your heels Driving you on long past agony and despair

name: The Hateful Accuser
flavourText: In truth, they point the finger at themselves.

name: The Will of Esh
flavourText: They whisper in the dark, building towers of mindless thought that seek a hollow truth.

name: The Felbog Fang
flavourText: Death creeps closer; unseen, inexorable, hungry.

name: The Ignomon
flavourText: The light that reveals is the glare that blinds.

name: The Will of Tul
flavourText: They hide in deep places, and hidden places, but stillness will find them... and bury them.

name: The Halcyon
flavourText: We wait, still as the dead. To join the great avalanche.

name: The Aylardex
flavourText: Shackled fires dance about; Might within from force without.

name: The Warden's Brand
flavourText: I don't always have a flame handy when a fresh delinquent walks through our gates.' - Brutus, Warden of Axiom

name: The Utmost
flavourText: He who stands on the loftiest peak is bound to be seen...

name: The Arkhon's Tools
flavourText: Motion, purpose... craft. The fruits of my mind laboured to build my wildest imaginings, never tiring, never faltering. Life... or something like it, engineered in its image.

name: The Untouched Soul
flavourText: Geomancy offered a safer way to use the Tears... but the Maji rejected that temptation as well.

name: The Adorned
flavourText: At their height, the Vaal glittered under the sun. A decade, a century, an aeon of prosperity... now nothing more than a passing wonder.

name: The Jinxed Juju
flavourText: Burned rhoa's eye and goatman's beard do demand: Leave behind those lazy bones; Dance, ye dead, at my command!

name: The Will of Uul-Netol
flavourText: They move and coil, gripped by painful ecstasy, all meaning long since lost to dead-eyed lust.

name: The Balance of Terror
flavourText: Fellshrine stood as a holy bastion opposite the Chamber of Sins, and all that it represented. For one to rise, the other must fall.

name: The Eternal Struggle
flavourText: Simply the way it must be, so that existence may be.

name: The Selfish Shepherd
flavourText: And when you are no longer useful, you will discover how much you truly mean.

name: The Will of Xoph
flavourText: They dance and scream under the Broken Sun as spiraling oblivion deepens into flame.

name: The Primordial Chain
flavourText: The leash of the lifegiver binds in both directions.

name: The Sundered Will
flavourText: They dream no longer, strive no longer, feel no longer. They dream only of continuing to dream, and know not why.

name: The Anvil
flavourText: Forge your Perseverance on the Anvil of Faith.

name: The Pariah
flavourText: A man who changes his loyalties often, soon finds he has none.

name: The Hungry Loop
flavourText: Be careful where you put your finger.

name: The Highwayman
flavourText: Somebody does have to get hurt.

name: The Ephemeral Bond
flavourText: For how little time they had together, their love was all the more powerful.

name: The Queller of Minds
flavourText: Quiet thy troubled soul. Think not. Just pray... to me.

name: The Anima Stone
flavourText: All revere the earth they walk, For it wields strength beyond compare, Holds knowledge more than thought, Stands long after all else falls.

name: The Golden Rule
flavourText: Hurt as you would be hurt.

name: The Druggery
flavourText: This will help with the pain. One for you... and one for me.' - Doctor 'Shaky Hands' Opden

name: The Red Nightmare
flavourText: We coagulate; a crimson shell that suffocates the unworthy.

name: The Front Line
flavourText: It was a great honour to fight at the front. The few that survived the initial charge were guaranteed fame and fortune.

name: The Siege
flavourText: As the dead battered Highgate's barricades, The Black Sekhema accepted her fate, And stood her ground.

name: The Green Dream
flavourText: We climb like vines up Chayula's arms, reaching into the world that should be ours.

name: The Green Nightmare
flavourText: We take root in the dirt and strangle those who tread upon it.

name: The Red Dream
flavourText: We flow like blood into Chayula's open mouth,and spill into the land we have watched forever.

name: The Burden of Truth
flavourText: Mortal pleasures can hold back the memories, but a hollow soul can never be healed.

name: The Tides of Time
flavourText: There is an ebb and flow to all things, tangible to those who watch and wait.

name: The Blue Nightmare
flavourText: We swell and flood and drown the undeserving beneath our might.

name: The Blue Dream
flavourText: We crash against Chayula's body, and fall like rain into the place we cannot go.

name: Melding of the Flesh
flavourText: We awoke to a sudden jungle rupturing the valleys of our home. Grasping limbs coiled around us, into us. We sank into each other, then rose into the living sky. My family screams alongside me still.

name: Original Sin
flavourText: Innocence rose to godhood not on inspired faith, but on the vilification and hatred of another.

name: The Light of Meaning
flavourText: To name a thing is to give it power.

name: The Magnate
flavourText: Few men cast a longer shadow than the Great Meginord of the North.

name: The Interrogation
flavourText: Pain is a fine motivator, But if you seek the truth, Fear of pain unknown has no parallel.

name: The Queen's Hunger
flavourText: In their crimson nightmare, the Vaal are still sacrificing themselves to her glory and beauty. They stab their own hearts and cry out in ecstasy, only to rise again.

name: The Coming Calamity
flavourText: Whiff of cold, tiny spark, faintest flicker in the dark. Embers swirl, ice takes form, sky exposed - Death's perfect storm. Frost and thunder, flames shine bright, ruin walks the land tonight. By your hand they dance and bend, wield them and brook no end.

name: The Apostate
flavourText: When I finally rejected my faith entirely, my stagnant belief became thick white blood, as choking as it was nourishing.

name: The Ivory Tower
flavourText: The mind is a filter through which anarchy becomes order.

name: The Three Dragons
flavourText: The ice seared his naked feet As the lightning stilled his heart, But it was the flames upon his lover's face That roused him to vengeance.' - From 'The Three Dragons' by Victario of Sarn

name: The Rat Cage
flavourText: The truth lies inside every man, if you dig around. Many a confession was found in the bowels of Axiom.

name: The Iron Fortress
flavourText: Stand steadfast in the face of destruction. The Council cannot afford to falter.' - Mauritius, the Iron Heart

name: The Restless Ward
flavourText: Use the dead to stave off death, An armour of bones and rot. Hanging on with bated breath, One lapse and all for naught.

name: The Admiral
flavourText: The Oriathans built their empire on naval mobility, which allowed them to wage war wherever their enemy was weakest.

name: The Hallowed Monarch
flavourText: I don't judge who you are, Saresh. I judge what you do. True leadership comes from fighting alongside those you command, from elevating them, and sharing the glory of victory. This, you will never understand.' - Sekhema Orbala, to be crowned Garukhan

name: The Embalmer
flavourText: Decomposition takes hold too quickly! No, if we are to keep the specimen in perfect shape, we must begin the process before expiry.

name: The Snowblind Grace
flavourText: We dance in the white, like water, colliding as many and emerging as one.

name: The Gull
flavourText: It is the Gull that delivers Man unto Ancestor. The consumer of our flesh. The seeder of our souls unto the earth. We give the Gull his life. The Gull gives us our Way.' - Lavianga, Advisor to Kaom

name: The Dark Monarch
flavourText: Hate? You speak to me of hate? You have no idea what your persecution inflicts. How it chokes the heart. Withers the soul. Judge me, and you judge yourself.' - Saresh, last words, to Sekhema Orbala

name: The Caged Mammoth
flavourText: The Cyclops of Trarthus became the star of the Oriath Arena, but he was merely biding his time, waiting for his chance...

name: The Fourth Vow
flavourText: Seek not to avoid the mortal pains of this world. In flagellation, there lies freedom from temptation.

name: The Eternity Shroud
flavourText: There can be no defence against the celestial siblings entropy and time.

name: The Blood Dance
flavourText: Sharks thrash and swirl To the pounding drum of their frenzied hearts As they dance in the waters red.' -Lavianga, Guardian of the Karui Way

name: The Beast Fur Shawl
flavourText: The quickest way to understand your own strengths and weaknesses is to walk in the skin of another.

name: The Perfect Form
flavourText: We share one space, speak one voice, act through one body. A flawless crystal. Brittle.

name: The Stampede
flavourText: Relentlessness. Nothing more, nothing less.

name: The Formless Flame
flavourText: Our skin turns to ash and we are swallowed by his brilliant red light.

name: The Formless Inferno
flavourText: He burns us to keep us from harm.

name: The Baron
flavourText: The Emperor's trusted surgeons are not the only ones who practice the dark arts. Some of us are just more discreet.

name: The Tempest Rising
flavourText: Where he tread, disintegrating storms of lightning and death laid waste to all around him.

name: The Red Trail
flavourText: We leave a trail, that we may know where never we will return.

name: The Infinite Pursuit
flavourText: We move to be closer to her, but the distance yet grows.

name: The Celestial Brace
flavourText: Forged from the heart of the densest star, your courage will fail long before it does.

name: The Vertex
flavourText: A queen should be seen, admired, but never touched.' - Atziri, Queen of the Vaal

name: The Brine Crown
flavourText: Greatest is the Brine King's domain, and every day it grows a little greater, not through force, but patience.

name: The Trickster's Smile
flavourText: The Raven Trickster made no move to defend himself. He merely grinned... and the foolish warrior charged.

name: The Hand of Phrecia
flavourText: To drive back the darkness, to bring peace, we must fight side by side as brothers.

name: The Bringer of Rain
flavourText: What lies beneath your feet?!' 'Sacred ground, watered with tears of blood!

name: The Devourer of Minds
flavourText: The Decay infects thought itself, leaving nothing but hollow husks filled with virulent void...

name: The Devouring Diadem
flavourText: The spirit hungers for the flesh.

name: The Broken Crown
flavourText: Every rule has an exception.

name: The Fledgling
flavourText: The single well-placed arrow that changes the world must be preceded by ten thousand practice shots.

name: Replica Atziri's Foible
flavourText: A rare unequivocal success, Prototype #11 causes wounds to heal so quickly the type Delta test subject actually survived the entire testing regimen.

name: Atziri's Foible
flavourText: The world is but a piece of parchment, blank and symmetric. We label each side: one Good, one Evil; one Black, one White. The divine truth, however, is that both are one and the same. -Jaetai, Vaal Advisor

name: Eye of Chayula
flavourText: Never blinking, always watching.

name: Kaom's Sign
flavourText: A token from the sea A sign for Kaom to lead his Karui to Wraeclast.

name: Shaper's Seed
flavourText: The first light to grow in the primordial darkness.

name: Kaom's Binding
flavourText: For centuries, he burned in an unending nightmare of lava and flame... but he endured.

name: Atziri's Reign
flavourText: Atziri went to great lengths to ensure her immortality, but nothing is eternal.

name: The Goddess Bound
flavourText: She paints her offer in wicked hues An off-white grin, an elegant bruise. To the nascent scourge she sings the ruse: 'With me in hand, what else need you use?

name: The Gluttonous Tide
flavourText: To eat, to feast, to forget the horror of endless agonizing existence if but for a moment... only to disgorge and do it all again...

name: The Gilded Chalice
flavourText: He took the newcomers' symbol and made it his own. Finally, they flocked to him. Finally, he had the power and wealth he so desired.' - Lycia, the Heretic

name: The Second Sacrament
flavourText: He took many of his people's traditions and gilded them, hollowed them. They rejected his new religion, and he and his followers were forced to depart the mountains for lands unknown.' - Lycia, the Heretic

name: The Chains of Castigation
flavourText: The mysterious traveller saw the vilified brother chained to a cliff, where all could point and shout and deride him. In one fell swing, she cracked the mountainside, freeing him.' - Lycia, the Heretic

name: The Blood of Innocence
flavourText: After weeks of being pursued, the veiled traveller made her stand in a sandstorm. Somehow, she wounded a god. Innocence relented; his brother and the traveller made good their escape.' - Lycia, the Heretic

name: The Broken Censer
flavourText: His followers were too small in number to spark divinity, so he turned to a greater power: hatred. He vilified his brother, sparking zealotry, and the change finally began.' - Lycia, the Heretic

name: The Living Blade
flavourText: Green-cloaked travelers emerged from the mists, planted a tree, and named it Lorrata. Its strongest root became a weapon...

name: The Coward's Trial
flavourText: For his sins he was hunted in his sleep, judgement wrought of twisted nightmare. The Coward bound his dreams to stone, awaiting another to walk the path of true atonement.

name: The Vinktar Square
flavourText: To the east, it cannot be seen. To the west, it cannot be touched. To the south, it cannot be remembered. And to the north, it cannot be contained.

name: The Writhing Jar
flavourText: To achieve godhood, they would cast off all that god has gifted us. Mortality, compassion, even the sanctity of flesh. - High Templar Voll

name: The Wise Oak
flavourText: The summer sun dries the soil and burns the leaves. The autumn rain extinguishes the flames. The spring bloom shades the wet earth. Nature is an eternal tug of war.

name: The First Crest
flavourText: In pursuit of divinity, he tried many times to found a religion. Few followed his initial symbols and proverbs. He needed something greater. A symbol none could deny.' - Lycia, the Heretic

name: The Hour of Divinity
flavourText: They ascended together, one unwillingly. The vilified became black as coal, and the lauded, golden. After a lifetime of ambition, he finally had his heart's desire. It only cost him his brother.' - Lycia, the Heretic

name: The Power and the Promise
flavourText: Building on the fear and hatred that deified him, Innocence threatened an eternity of flames for nonbelievers. The newcomers wailed and threw themselves at his feet in the thousands.' - Lycia, the Heretic

name: The Eternal Apple
flavourText: The empire is both the tree and the fruit. It provides safe harbour as ideas grow within, and when the time is right, the apple is picked. The idea, and our ideals, take root.

name: The Monastery Bell
flavourText: We must be ready. We are the voice of Wraeclast's vengeance, tolling righteous fury for those who would dare invade our world!' - Ailith, First of the Keepers

name: The Night Lamp
flavourText: The newcomers were terrified of fire. He used their fear to control them, to lay the seeds of unquestioning faith. He claimed only his god could protect them.' - Lycia, the Heretic

name: The Original Scripture
flavourText: It's all here. The lie at the core of my faith. Maxarius was not the first chosen of Innocence. Maxarius was Innocence himself. A charlatan, a liar, and a power-seeker.' - Lycia, the Heretic

name: The Goddess Scorned
flavourText: Her purpose seems done; the oath is fulfilled. Rust dulls her smirk with the last demon killed. The embers grow dim and yet hope burns her lips: 'An old flame renewed can define our eclipse!

name: The Grey Wind
flavourText: Silence fell... we gazed upon high. The Red Pyre flared, palms wide. Ash-laden gales scoured our flesh. Four screams became one roar.

name: The Consuming Dark
flavourText: The brightest flames cast the darkest shadows.

name: The Whispering Ice
flavourText: Guard your darkest thoughts well, for they are the cracks through which the Nightmare crawls.

name: The Dancing Dervish
flavourText: Take your partner by the hand, Keep your steps in time. Swing together, spin apart, And dance with death sublime.

name: The Deep One's Hide
flavourText: The thicker the shell, the greater the beast that hunts it.

name: The Winds of Fate
flavourText: Life... Death... The whim of the cosmos.

name: The Supreme Truth
flavourText: Knowledge brings power, and with power you can grab truth by the throat and shape it as you wish.

name: The Stormheart
flavourText: When the storm comes, the safest place to be is the centre.

name: The Ghastly Theatre
flavourText: Never let the audience know your true form. Misdirect them, beguile them. Strike when they least expect it.

name: The Grey Spire
flavourText: There was never a simpler time. Just simpler motivations.

name: The Princess
flavourText: She's pretty, aye. So pretty you'll want to be with her long after you're dead.

name: The Fulcrum
flavourText: To stand at the confluence of the elements, the master must achieve perfect balance.

name: The Annihilating Light
flavourText: There is no force more destructive in the heavens than the scintillating light of utter clarity.

name: The Wasp Nest
flavourText: To discover how cruel nature can be, you need only shake the wrong branch.

name: The Putrid Cloister
flavourText: Please take out your blades, your whips, and your spikes. Class is now in session.

name: The Black Cane
flavourText: Lead the army of the damned from the front.

name: The Flawed Refuge
flavourText: The Wildwood was a gift, meant as a haven against the Winter of the World.

name: The Golden Charlatan
flavourText: He speaks, he leads, he stands tall... yet, what has he truly done, save spill our blood in pursuit of power?

name: The Crimson Storm
flavourText: There were no survivors. It had only been fired twice.' - Order of the Djinn inscription

name: The Blood Thorn
flavourText: Touch not the thorn, for only blood and pain await.

name: The Twilight Temple
flavourText: In the shadow of war, all are eclipsed.

name: The Poised Prism
flavourText: What do you see when you look inward?

name: The Hidden Blade
flavourText: The shadow warrior moves like the wind; his strikes land long after he is gone.

name: The Burden of Shadows
flavourText: Nothingness is loathe to relinquish its grip. Every moment is a struggle to exist.

name: The Harvest
flavourText: Let it grow and gather inside them, Let it flow through their veins. Don't waste a drop.

name: The Saviour
flavourText: On the mirrored edge of infinity, one man sinks forever into darkness, one man rises into light. But which one am I?

name: The Tempestuous Steel
flavourText: The blade thrums with wild energy Eager for vengeance against all who walk free.

name: The Oppressor
flavourText: Every clash leaves one more scar.

name: The Poet's Pen
flavourText: In every piece of prose, lies a tiny spark of magic.

name: The Anticipation
flavourText: We are within her reach, and when the time is right, she will reach into us.

name: The Screaming Eagle
flavourText: The eagle knows nothing but the scream and the strike.

name: The Overflowing Chalice
flavourText: Empty cup, full of promise.

name: The Surrender
flavourText: Our hearts cry out but are silenced by our flesh and so we give up our flesh.

name: The Scourge
flavourText: With increasing mastery over death comes an increasing desire for it.

name: The Scales of Justice
flavourText: You shall be weighed and measured. You shall be judged... and perhaps you shall be found worthy.

name: The Sorrow of the Divine
flavourText: As man sins, God weeps.

name: The Searing Touch
flavourText: Burn to cinders, scar and maim, Rule a world, bathed in flame.

name: The Iron Mass
flavourText: Lead by example.

name: The Battle Within
flavourText: The struggle for balance never ends.

name: The Blood Reaper
flavourText: To cease the flow of blood is to choke the rain in the very clouds. Both life and land feel the thirst.

name: Shaper's Touch
flavourText: By my hand, the inert is given life. By my hand, that which rots is reborn. There is nothing that cannot be changed. Nothing.

name: Replica Kaom's Heart
flavourText: Useless for our purposes, but perhaps we can sell Prototype #5 to an archmage to fund other experiments.

name: Kaom's Command
flavourText: Kaom ordered the desecration of the Empire's dead. There would be no rest or honours for the wicked.

name: Atziri's Acuity
flavourText: The heart is the herald. It will tell me when it is best to strike.' - Atziri, Queen of the Vaal

name: Kaom's Roots
flavourText: Don't flinch. It's a waste of good hitting time.

name: Replica Atziri's Acuity
flavourText: One of our researchers cut himself on Prototype #2, and he has not stopped screaming for months...

name: Kaom's Spirit
flavourText: Who can tell when whispers are truly from a god?

name: Night's Hold
flavourText: In the light of Solaris, the shadows cower and hide. But every night they gather and grow, and all but the strong and the stupid seek shelter from their grasp until daybreak.

name: Ngamahu's Sign
flavourText: A gift from Ngamahu, a sign to the Karui to spread like fire. Given to Akoya, but inherited by Kaom with the swing of his axe.

name: Soulbound
flavourText: Slay my twin and I will inherit her wisdom. Slay me and her life will be prolonged by my demise. Our souls are eternally bound by the sacrifices we have made.' - High Priest Atazek

name: Bonemeld
flavourText: Hills of stark and jagged white it walks, scratching your ribs without, within. The Fiend has naught but Empty Eyes, though sees you, it does, indeed.

name: Natural Hierarchy
flavourText: Just as the rat cowers before the dog and the dog cowers before Man, so too should we cower before the First Ones and pray we never learn of what comes next.

name: Berek's Grip
flavourText: Berek hid from Storm's lightning wrath In the embrace of oblivious Frost Repelled by ice, blinded by blizzards Storm raged in vain While Berek slept.' - Berek and the Untamed

name: Berek's Pass
flavourText: From Frost's ice-bound pass Berek taunted and jeered Until furious Flame scaled the mountain Berek escaped through the thaw And Frost's tortured moans.' - Berek and the Untamed

name: Mutewind Seal
flavourText: When a fallen leader's body is taken to the funeral peak, those who seek power must ascend together. One returns with the seal. The rest do not return at all.

name: Betrayal's Sting
flavourText: It is not a wound caused by an enemy that bites us twice. It is the smile, the nod... the handshake... of a former friend.

name: Replica Tasalio's Sign
flavourText: Likely our closest to the original, yet Prototype #22 still falls short. Are these objects actually somehow resisting our efforts?

name: Venarius' Astrolabe
flavourText: You grew up an orphan, and for that, you blame me. Fair enough. So... why not let me erase that pain from your mind? Then we can all stand united against the demons at the door...

name: Praxis
flavourText: The Thaumaturgical masters of the Eternal Empire, as unpredictable and varied as they were, all understood one thing: Free thinking leads to free action.

name: Rigwald's Curse
flavourText: I once thought the First Ones were just stories made to scare children. But I've seen what they can do. I've felt it. And now I must live with that terrible knowledge.

name: Maligaro's Cruelty
flavourText: He does not love. He does not feel regret or remorse. He does not think about consequences, only possibilities. If that does not describe a monster, tell me: what does?' - Archbishop Geofri

name: Brinerot Mark
flavourText: Each time, it is granted to the most senior captain of the fleet, and each time, the ring soon washes ashore once more, still wrapped around a severed finger.

name: Star of Wraeclast
flavourText: I offer to you an eternal oath that binds your heart to mine; a bond that not even death will break. Will you accept?' - Daresso, to his beloved

name: Defiance of Destiny
flavourText: The farmer was struck again and again, but he refused to stay down. Astonished, the raiding warlord ordered the man's family spared.

name: Blood of Corruption
flavourText: In my dream, a voice spoke to me. It said: 'My reach knows no bounds. All that is pure is destined to rot. All that lives is destined to serve.' - Doryani, Queen's Thaumaturgist

name: Shavronne's Revelation
flavourText: Shavronne held Sanity in her right hand and Revelation in her left. Brutus chose the left hand.' - Kadavrus, Surgeon to the Umbra

name: Blightwell
flavourText: Long ago, the ocean was a puddle where a golden fish dwelt, who lit the ocean from within and kept the water fresh. When the sky burned, the fish dived deep, never to return, and the waters turned sour.

name: Thief's Torment
flavourText: The ring I stole, My finger they took, A shrouded mind, Cut their curses short, As I drained their spirit And stole their soul. A blessing is often a curse.

name: Uzaza's Valley
flavourText: Sheltered beneath thick ice, the river ferried fat fish towards the sea. But the First King knew the river's secret, and the fish were not the only ones who grew fat.

name: Bloodsoaked Medallion
flavourText: Atziri ordained that we exploit the weaknesses inherent in our slaves. With relish, we did exactly as she instructed.' - Guatelitzi, Architect of Flesh

name: Perandus Signet
flavourText: Our warehouses are bursting. Our vaults are full. But our minds are still hungry.' - Medici Perandus, Prefect to the Treasury

name: Circle of Anguish
flavourText: I condemned an innocent man to the pyres, but to admit this mistake is to condemn myself. My only choice is to strive harder.

name: Uzaza's Meadow
flavourText: Cold winds blasted what little grew on the icy surface. The gifts of the land lay hidden deeper, and only patience and persistence would free them.

name: Circle of Guilt
flavourText: I feel the moral weight of what I must to do to protect Wraeclast. I accept my guilt without shame. It is my gift to humanity.

name: Tainted Pact
flavourText: Beidat made false promises to many denizens Converting only one into a conduit Through which Wraeclast might be consumed.

name: Ahkeli's Valley
flavourText: The river, once fertile and fresh, and flowing briskly to the sea, now stood, stained, at a standstill. Dammed by the coagulating dead.

name: Replica Winterheart
flavourText: Researcher Graven spent eleven hours suffering electrocution in the lab before he was found. Prototype #14 somehow kept him from dying.

name: Uzaza's Mountain
flavourText: The narrow path turned to rough rocks that led towards the sky. One last obstacle in a life-long journey to find a land they could call home.

name: Putembo's Meadow
flavourText: The fields were silent but for the plucking of fruits, the rustling of leaves, and the breaking of stone. No slave dared to speak or look the passing king in the eye. No one... except Aul.

name: Replica Dragonfang's Flight
flavourText: Did we make this? Why do we have no record of it? We were warned that there would be consequences...' - Administrator Qotra

name: Prospero's Protection
flavourText: Worry not, my friend, that I tour in fineries. The ostentation is all part of being a Perandus. As long as I maintain my Vigilance, nothing can harm the Empire... or me.' - Emperor Chitus, to Ondar

name: Vivinsect
flavourText: Fusing the parasite with another ring has manifested unpredictable effects. I theorise the sacrificial vessel's level of anguish is a key variable. - Arzaak, Syndicate Researcher

name: Heartbound Loop
flavourText: When the axe finally fell, Seryl shared his pain, and the last thought that flickered through his fading mind was her broken, shattered scream.

name: Leadership's Price
flavourText: Remain poised. Remain balanced. Keep all the emotions of a lifetime caged. Let only your enemies see the truth of your rage.

name: Putembo's Mountain
flavourText: He surveyed his lands, green and vital, watched with pride as his slaves quarried fine stone for his fortress, and thanked the heavens for his many blessings. But this pilgrimage to the peak was to be his last.

name: Tasalio's Sign
flavourText: A gift from Tasalio, God of Water, to the chieftain Rakiata. Kaom took Rakiata's head and hand so that his warriors' axes might rise and fall like the waves.

name: Replica Doedre's Damning
flavourText: Prototype #8 makes it difficult to think negatively, but two fatalities resulted when a lead researcher used an epithet in its presence.

name: Icefang Orbit
flavourText: Those members of the Brotherhood who employ the venom of Trarthan ice snakes must take great care with the volatile substance.

name: Astramentis
flavourText: Mindless rage will shake the world, Cunning lies will bend it. Reckless haste will break the world, And into darkness send it.

name: Replica Emberwake
flavourText: The flames raced through Lab Five with incredible speed, but were extinguished just as quickly. This could have been much worse.' - Lead Researcher Ksaret

name: Voll's Devotion
flavourText: We are the soldiers of Faith, armoured in devotion. Let the sinners come, for we - the Pure - shall endure!' - Voll of Thebrus, at the Battle of the Bridge

name: Ahkeli's Meadow
flavourText: Where once had stood a village, lay naught but splinters. Some had once been her home. Some had once been her creations. Some had once been her family.

name: Eye of Innocence
flavourText: ...and so He said: 'Let only the good meet my gaze' and no eye met His. So He called down the cleansing flames and let black smoke sweep the Sinners away.' - Book of Innocence

name: Essence Worm
flavourText: This thing is not a pet. It is a parasite that feeds on the very will of its host. Like any part of nightmare, it has found a way to make its price... acceptable.' - Malachai the Soulless

name: Replica Badge of the Brotherhood
flavourText: “I stood upon the tower's edge, and saw that we had cracked the sky. There is nowhere we can run that our sins will not find us now.” - Researcher Arn, last recorded words

name: Replica Hyrri's Truth
flavourText: The type Delta test subjects could have escaped with the power offered by Prototype #15, but they suddenly chose to murder each other instead...

name: Tear of Purity
flavourText: A shimmering symbol of Purity, clear as water, but I know better than most how quickly Purity can succumb to Corruption. How quickly water turns to blood. - Victario, the People's Poet

name: Warped Timepiece
flavourText: As you have lived, so you shall die forever trying to keep up with me. Your blood on these hands of mine forever makes me the public enemy.

name: Tavukai
flavourText: Hyrri and her arrows broke the sacred code, damning herself. Kaom seized her sacrifice, and in doing so, seized victory.' - Lavianga, Advisor to Kaom

name: Replica Malachai's Artifice
flavourText: As much as Prototype #20 hints at some deep alternate physics, we cannot afford to expend any more test subjects. Experiments halted.' - Administrator Qotra

name: Putembo's Valley
flavourText: With no stone for rebuilding, each storm took its toll on the village. Huts eventually collapsed, their occupants injured or dead. Bodies were left by the river, to appease the gods. But the dead would not remain there.

name: Lori's Lantern
flavourText: By its light, Lori led her young charges to safety and bound up their wounds. Her sword arm was iron, yet her heart gentle and proof against hate.

name: Replica Hinekora's Sight
flavourText: I touched #2993, and I saw... how blind we've been. The visions weren't the future. They were the past! Our 'unforeseen consequences' have already been happening!' - Researcher Graven

name: Eyes of the Greatwolf
flavourText: I am but a vessel for a greater force. It acts through me. Speaks through me. Decides what lives and dies through me. And will change the world through me.

name: Lost Unity
flavourText: All gates are closed. All dreams are silenced. What could have been...

name: Perquil's Toe
flavourText: He was a lot luckier before he lost this.

name: Replica Prismweave
flavourText: A legion of forty soldiers attempted to break into Outpost Five and steal Prototype #659. What do they know that we do not?

name: Soulthirst
flavourText: They say a draught of fine spirits will ward off the elements and promote a longer, merrier life. I have found this to be true on all counts.' - Zerphi of the Vaal

name: Replica Primordial Might
flavourText: The summoned golems immediately battered through the chamber wall and killed several guards, but their fury only lasted a short time.

name: Venopuncture
flavourText: There is a way to survive the bite of an ice snake, but few have the resolve to attempt it.

name: Storm Secret
flavourText: Lightning lives in an endless circle.

name: Daresso's Salute
flavourText: A bit short in the arm, are you? Then you'll be short of a head soon enough.' - Daresso the Daring

name: Death Rush
flavourText: To truly appreciate life you must be there when it ends

name: Replica Soul Tether
flavourText: Curious. The test spike penetrated the subject's flesh, but the chest wound was not as deep as expected. There is something here...

name: Dead Reckoning
flavourText: A mage from the coast rode up on a broken nag, legs burnt to his bones. Before he collapsed, he uttered: 'I watched the world we know end yesterday.

name: Replica Siegebreaker
flavourText: Recommend extreme caution on any prototypes that can lead to a chain reaction of deaths. Lab Twelve has been lost to the flames.' - Lead Researcher Ksaret

name: Astral Projector
flavourText: The body stands, but the spirit soars.

name: Polaric Devastation
flavourText: Those that escaped the annihilating light sank eternally into crushing darkness.

name: Mark of Submission
flavourText: So great was the thaumaturgy of a bloodpriest's mark, that sacrifices soon welcomed their death.

name: Bisco's Leash
flavourText: You were always there, by my side, whether we sat or played. Our friendship was a joyful ride, I wish you could have stayed.

name: Squirming Terror
flavourText: Madness crawls under the skin, bursting forth from the flesh.

name: Extractor Mentis
flavourText: When slaughtered flesh falls silent, the soul may yet scream on.

name: Careful Planning
flavourText: Greatly outnumbered, Deshret dressed her personal guard in identical garb. When the Empire rode north, Deshret and her guard took turns revealing themselves, creating the illusion of speed beyond the capabilities of even the Virtue Gems.' - History of the Maraketh

name: Hyrri's Truth
flavourText: Strike true, strike hard, and leave no survivors to retaliate.

name: Winterheart
flavourText: Those who dwell in the deep freeze enjoy a special kind of madness.

name: Pyre
flavourText: Let winter come. It will only make my fire burn brighter.

name: Marylene's Fallacy
flavourText: Marylene stroked the medallion at her breast before every duel and every cast of the die.' - Victario, the People's Poet

name: Replica Powerlessness
flavourText: The suppression troops have stopped responding to my orders. I'm no longer in charge, and I likely never truly was... I suspect they're already coming for us.' - Lead Researcher Ksaret, one hour post-Incident

name: Dissolution of the Flesh
flavourText: We awoke to a sudden dawn cresting through the mountains. Each peak rose into searing fire, a massive roiling tide. A great eye gazed upon us, and we became known - utterly.

name: Stone of Lazhwar
flavourText: You are slow, foolish and ignorant. I am not.

name: Enmity's Embrace
flavourText: In truth, your terror is cold You mask it with heat and ire But they know. They know.

name: Eternal Damnation
flavourText: The price of immortality is isolation.

name: Dream Fragments
flavourText: Doryani stumbled into a realm of madness And awoke its Master.

name: Feastbind
flavourText: Our forefathers danced and drank and ate their fill and did not honour the First Ones for their gifts. So the First Ones filled the sky with fire.

name: Araku Tiki
flavourText: It is said to make you invisible when the Great Spirit comes to take you on your final journey.

name: Malachai's Artifice
flavourText: When the wind blows, Know which way to bend and watch the others break.

name: Fated End
flavourText: All roads lead to that destined doom.

name: Rashkaldor's Patience
flavourText: Fate's smile, man's ruin.

name: Replica Voideye
flavourText: So close, yet frustratingly distinct. Something more is going on here...

name: Snakepit
flavourText: They wrap around you until your blood turns as cold as theirs.

name: Le Heup of All
flavourText: Existence is infinite A weave of the living and dead Beyond the understanding Of the many mortal threads

name: Profane Proxy
flavourText: The machines do not hate. They merely serve one who does.

name: Doedre's Damning
flavourText: Where her mouth should have been there was only a whirling, black void.

name: Valyrium
flavourText: They will rise and fall in fire and blood.

name: Blackflame
flavourText: Beyond the veil of death, there burns a fire by whose light night is borne.

name: Faminebind
flavourText: After the Great Fire, the land lay barren and our forefathers grew weak. Mother Gull took pity on them and gave them grain and water.

name: Doedre's Tongue
flavourText: Maligaro did the cutting... at her request. In the new void, a malevolent power emerged.

name: Replica Pacifism
flavourText: Release the Type Delta test subjects. Unseal all prototype lockers. Arm yourself! I know that, as researchers, you've never had to fight before, but they're coming to kill us all. It's resist or die!' - Lead Researcher Ksaret, two hours post-Incident

name: Victario's Acuity
flavourText: Grind your words into sharp thoughts. Grind your thoughts into the sharpest of deeds.' - Victario, the People's Poet

name: Stormfire
flavourText: When your skin sloughs, and your blood cooks, you'll wish the lightning strike had killed you.

name: Coiling Whisper
flavourText: I never knew fear until she was ripped away. My promises were hollow ever after.

name: Emberwake
flavourText: Leave the world in flames behind you.

name: Stranglegasp
flavourText: Death's approach brings clarity.

name: Voideye
flavourText: The darker the eye, the more diligent the watched.

name: Soul Tether
flavourText: Vaal bloodpriests were among the earliest intellectuals on record. It was they who found that a newly freed soul would desperately cling to any other source of life.

name: Valako's Sign
flavourText: A gift from Valako, appointing Kiloava as the Herald of War. A title Kaom claimed when he ended Kiloava's bloodline.

name: Bloodgrip
flavourText: Combat is simple. Keep your blood in. Take theirs out.

name: Tawhanuku's Timing
flavourText: The soul still beats, even when the heart never did.

name: Blackheart
flavourText: Fear is highly infectious.

name: Firesong
flavourText: Within a firestorm, the Thane commands the flames Emblazoned by glory and the song of the First Ones For the master of fire fears nothing.

name: Voice of the Storm
flavourText: When she of many mouths spoke, we bowed in awe and were crushed.

name: Fertile Mind
flavourText: The swallow flew fast and took many turns, spilling a seed where no plant had grown before. This seed grew and grew until the desert became fertile and abundant. Your mind is like this seed.' - Maraketh Proverb

name: Sidhebreath
flavourText: The breath of life is yours to give.

name: Fury Valve
flavourText: A single act of anger travels countless paths of destruction.

name: Kikazaru
flavourText: Hear no evil.

name: Warrior's Legacy
flavourText: Make your mark on history

name: Angler's Plait
flavourText: A man can spend his whole life fishing before he learns it is not fish that he seeks.

name: Romira's Banquet
flavourText: The Empress gave Romira two sons Born of his brother's seed Romira threw her a banquet A perfidious meal indeed.

name: Circle of Regret
flavourText: I sacrificed a life of love for one of responsibility, so that she, and others like her, might be kept safe.

name: Andvarius
flavourText: Danger is the price of wealth.

name: Ungil's Harmony
flavourText: Gentle anger, raging calm.

name: Circle of Nostalgia
flavourText: I was a happy child, before the cruel truth was revealed to me. I fight so that the children may remain ignorant.

name: Rigwald's Crest
flavourText: Within the heart of every man and woman lies the soul of a ferocious beast. If you cannot tame it, embrace it.

name: Ancestral Vision
flavourText: The spirits of our ancestors guided us from the Archipelago to the continent. Inextricably, the purity of our souls is linked to the ones who came before us.

name: Whispers of Infinity
flavourText: In the Atlas, you do not go mad. You are rewritten.

name: Anathema
flavourText: Enraged by the incompetence of mortals The demon-lord opens a gateway Unleashing a litany of pain upon the world.

name: Zerphi's Heart
flavourText: We are incapable of change without sacrifice, for we are both the iron and the forge.

name: Rational Doctrine
flavourText: Logic wanes in shining faith, and in rationalism, ardour dims Thus, the cynic and the zealot are divided But can they not be one and the same?

name: Grattus Signet
flavourText: The first Grattus patriarch had only one tell. When he slowly turned his ring, all cowered before him.

name: Choir of the Storm
flavourText: But the fool did not bow. The fool stood and questioned. And the fool was unwritten.

name: Rotblood Promise
flavourText: Accept the infection, let it take hold. Then carry it far and wide.

name: Gloomfang
flavourText: Darkness never stops feeding.

name: Replica Karui Ward
flavourText: In testing, Prototype #9 had no effect on fired arrows. However, an unknown spell did destroy the entire firing chamber.

name: Karui Ward
flavourText: Shoot first, ask no questions.' - Karui wisdom

name: Willowgift
flavourText: The storm cannot break that which bends.

name: Ming's Heart
flavourText: Ming slew Tranquillity Took Chaos for his wife And on Her immortal finger He placed his Heart

name: Gifts from Above
flavourText: God blesses those who bless themselves.

name: Circle of Fear
flavourText: My subordinates circled me eternally, attuned to the slightest weakness, ready to tear me apart for their own gains.

name: Yoke of Suffering
flavourText: Let the unrepentant be dragged ever downwards by the weight of their sins.

name: Sibyl's Lament
flavourText: The portrait reflected his pain, a pain that she could never see.

name: Circle of Ambition
flavourText: I will build the wall that stands against the tide. The day is coming... I have seen it.

name: Immortal Flesh
flavourText: She begged the Earth to spare her Son; Out of love the Earth agreed. To the other Elements she did not speak And out of spite They plotted.' - Berek and the Untamed

name: Chain of Endurance
flavourText: A man confronted with sufficient adversity may ascend to unprecedented heights and triumph over his coddled rivals.' - Weylan the Ezomyte

name: Replica Fragility
flavourText: Our defenses are failing at Outpost One. We can't hold out much longer. All outposts, abandon your stations! Escape while you can!' - Lead Researcher Ksaret, three hours post-Incident

name: Ikiaho's Promise
flavourText: Even the loneliest of souls can aid a friend in times of darkness.

name: Carnage Heart
flavourText: Forged from the blood of countless wars, its thirst has only begun.

name: Nevalius Inheritance
flavourText: I come from a long line of scholars, poets, and artists. You can imagine how little we leave our children... My father only gifted me one thing: for good or ill, I don't know when to quit.' - Victario Nevalius, the People's Poet

name: Redblade Band
flavourText: To ascend to leadership, the child of a Redblade warlord must pull the band from the still-hot ashes of their father.

name: Mokou's Embrace
flavourText: Fire makes the perfect blossom in the endless night.

name: Timeclasp
flavourText: To us mere mortals, time is slippery. I'm just evening things out.' - Doryani, Queen's Thaumaturgist

name: Witchbane
flavourText: In darkest night, 'neath waxen moon A witch snatches a boy from his room. He wards off her hexes The witch he perplexes And so becomes part of her stew.

name: Retaliation Charm
flavourText: An eye for an eye.

name: Replica Bated Breath
flavourText: I cannot fathom the mysteries of Prototype #16. It did nearly nothing until I brought it to [RESTRICTED]. It makes no sense!' - Researcher Graven

name: Sacrificial Heart
flavourText: The seed of life, saved and savoured.

name: Ixchel's Temptation
flavourText: Chaos offers possibility, not outcome. Our own imaginations ensnare us.

name: Winterweave
flavourText: Fury fuels defiance.

name: Transcendent Mind
flavourText: A keen mind sees what others do not, makes connections where others do not, and is dangerous in a way that others are not.

name: Xoph's Heart
flavourText: His is our heart. To its beat we are all driven.

name: Woespike
flavourText: The old wound lurks deep within, never healing, never relenting, making every smile half-hearted.

name: Replica Headhunter
flavourText: A type Delta test subject escaped with Prototype #18. He was last seen ten times the height of a man and crashing straight through walls.

name: Call of the Brotherhood
flavourText: Forged by three brothers so that they may recognize each other across any distance of time or travel.

name: Call of the Void
flavourText: Only when the mind is empty of ambition can the cold truth of existence take hold.

name: Kalandra's Touch
flavourText: On one hand, you have a choice. On the other, you have its twin.

name: Ahkeli's Mountain
flavourText: Fleeing the destruction set upon her home, the Clayshaper sought safety in the clouds of ash above.

name: Seething Fury
flavourText: It took the Bloody Flowers Rebellion to show the clans of Ezomyr the truth; What kept them apart was just a fabrication. Conjured rivalries from men who grew fat from the discord they sowed.

name: Xoph's Blood
flavourText: We are his blood. Through us he carries his burning message.

name: Calamitous Visions
flavourText: Try as I might, I could not escape it. When I closed my eyes, I saw only death. Each breath tainted with the scent of seared and smouldering flesh, And each sound tangled with pleas for mercy.

name: Uul-Netol's Vow
flavourText: The time is nigh. War has come. We dream as one.

name: Haunting Memories
flavourText: We cannot hide from the wounds of youth. They fuel the fires within in, driving us on.

name: Nimis
flavourText: Too much of something is bad enough; too much of nothing is just as tough.

name: Hinekora's Sight
flavourText: Remember the past, anticipate the future.

name: Apex Mode
flavourText: Maximum power fueled by science gone mad.

name: Dyadian Dawn
flavourText: With her cold resolve And burning sacrifice The Eternal twins arose.

name: Energy From Within
flavourText: The Azmeri ascetics learnt the power of going without the body's ordinary cravings.

name: Emperor's Mastery
flavourText: Learn as much as you can,and surround yourself with people who know the rest.

name: Ascent From Flesh
flavourText: A single step forward Snap free from the prison Reborn into freedom eternal

name: Voices
flavourText: Only a madman would ignore a god's instructions.

name: Coward's Legacy
flavourText: Death is your most important duty. Face it, or curse your bloodline for all eternity.

name: Inertia
flavourText: There is no force without movement.

name: Efficient Training
flavourText: Working smart and working hard aren't mutually exclusive.

name: Arn's Anguish
flavourText: The tortured thinker is made heavier by the weight of his guilt.

name: Elegant Hubris
flavourText: They believed themselves better than the past, but that confidence brought about nightmare.

name: Forbidden Flesh
flavourText: The bodies of those wholly subsumed by the Tangle continue to merge and mutate and cry out for release...

name: Fortress Covenant
flavourText: Forsake what you might have had. Command power beyond your potential.

name: Fragility
flavourText: Your flesh will fail you.

name: Belt of the Deceiver
flavourText: In battle, virtue matters not. Only victory.

name: Binds of Bloody Vengeance
flavourText: What once marked his submission became the tool of his defiance - torn from the lash of House Keita.

name: Bear's Girdle
flavourText: Simple. Deadly. Unstoppable

name: Energised Armour
flavourText: I've yet to see prayer stop an arrow.

name: Emperor's Cunning
flavourText: The greatest victories happen before the battle has begun.

name: Emperor's Wit
flavourText: The greatest victories happen before the battle has begun.

name: Amanamu's Gaze
flavourText: The Liege of the Lightless seeks dominion over the surface dwellers.

name: Emperor's Might
flavourText: The greatest victories happen before the battle has begun.

name: Healthy Mind
flavourText: For the ambitious, flesh is a limitation.

name: Wurm's Molt
flavourText: They say a lifetime of wisdom is carried in every skin the great beasts shed.

name: Coward's Chains
flavourText: As a gift or as punishment, the Empire will have your blood.

name: Gluttony
flavourText: What started as a desire to feed became a desire to learn...

name: Bound By Destiny
flavourText: The future weaves ever forward, twisting into itself forever, driven by the passions and tragedies of those who seek.

name: Bound Fate
flavourText: Knowing what will happen and knowing when it will happen are two very different things.

name: Bloodnotch
flavourText: At the core of the warrior's spirit, a fierce determination burns, igniting their capacity to endure.

name: Chains of Emancipation
flavourText: Freedom is won only by those who are not free.

name: Graven's Secret
flavourText: The cowardly thinker's greatest success is simply surviving.

name: Chill of Corruption
flavourText: Even a millennium later, Atziri's presence casts a shroud over Wraeclast.

name: Umbilicus Immortalis
flavourText: The power of rebirth rivals that of immortality.' - Icius Perandus, Antiquities Collection, Item 3

name: Unending Hunger
flavourText: They roamed, they fed, they grew, Killing as they went, Conquer though they may, Their hearts will never be content.

name: Ulaman's Gaze
flavourText: The Sovereign of the Well seeks dominion over the light.

name: Perandus Blazon
flavourText: A large enough debt turns even a friend into an enemy, and the Perandus family had more debtors than anyone.

name: Ceinture of Benevolence
flavourText: Put your faith in me. Our god demands it.' - High Templar Maxarius.

name: Transcendent Flesh
flavourText: We are as much shaped by what we do as what is done to us.

name: Transcendent Spirit
flavourText: Take comfort knowing that, even in death, we may serve our Queen and fuel her empire.

name: Ynda's Stand
flavourText: When all else was burning and overrun, she held the bridge to the very end.

name: Hidden Potential
flavourText: The difference between the master and his apprentice is what they see when they look at the same block of wood.

name: To Dust
flavourText: In the end, time comes for all of us. It just comes for some much sooner.

name: Immutable Force
flavourText: How simple a power, on which empires turn, when one man stands firm and says, 'I refuse.

name: Hyperboreus
flavourText: Cold winds whirl at the crown of the world.

name: Brute Force Solution
flavourText: Picking a lock takes an immense amount of skill and practice. Breaking it with a hammer takes about three seconds.

name: Pacifism
flavourText: Your fear will overcome you.

name: Tempered Spirit
flavourText: Though the body rots, the spirit lives on.

name: Meginord's Girdle
flavourText: Kaom's strength was rivaled only by the great Meginord of the north.

name: Pure Talent
flavourText: The skilled know how to learn. The talented know who to learn from.

name: Olesya's Delight
flavourText: The cruel thinker finds glee in torture most precise.

name: Quickening Covenant
flavourText: Lose that which you never had. Gain power you could not have grasped.

name: Might of the Meek
flavourText: Enough mice can kill a wolf.

name: Kurgal's Gaze
flavourText: The Blackblooded seeks dominion over darkness itself.

name: Siegebreaker
flavourText: Poison the land and they'll have nothing to defend.

name: Rain of Splinters
flavourText: If one is an annoyance then a hundred is a threat.' - Ancient Karui Proverb

name: Leash of Oblation
flavourText: Those who offer up sacrifices to every deity entreat the full favour of none.

name: Intuitive Leap
flavourText: The carpenter who picks up a blade is not mad. He's ambitious.

name: Primordial Might
flavourText: Do not cause the land to stir, It holds secrets better unknown.' - Azmerian proverb

name: One With Nothing
flavourText: Once you begin to rely on your weapons, You ensure you can't live without them.

name: Inspired Learning
flavourText: If you do not learn from a won battle then you have already lost the war.

name: Tecrod's Gaze
flavourText: The Hated Slave seeks dominion over his own kind.

name: Primordial Eminence
flavourText: Kings fall, empires crumble, mortals perish. All turn to earth and sand.' - Maraketh proverb

name: Maligaro's Restraint
flavourText: Our genius will pave the way forward. May all who are worthy be improved!' - Inquisitor Maligaro

name: Replica Reckless Defence
flavourText: Prototype #298 must be contained in a non-conductive glass box at all times.

name: Prismweave
flavourText: Nothing is as vivid as the rage of battle

name: Primordial Harmony
flavourText: A stone is not a stone, It is but one part of a fortress.' - Ezomyte proverb

name: Ryslatha's Coil
flavourText: All creatures have the potential for greatness or unequivocal failure.

name: Kitava's Teachings
flavourText: Savour the bitter, cherish the sweet, For there may never be another chance to eat.

name: Sublime Vision
flavourText: This world is not good enough for Zana|her, so I will make a better one. Nothing matters but the pursuit of perfection.

name: Fevered Mind
flavourText: In sickness, the insane becomes sane.

name: Pyroshock Clasp
flavourText: Teach a man to burn, and you'll be warm for the rest of his life.

name: Survivor's Guilt
flavourText: The burden falls heaviest not on those that died, but on those that did not.

name: Nadir Mode
flavourText: Indiscriminate destruction fueled by science gone mad.

name: Cyclopean Coil
flavourText: With the patience of a prowling lion, the Shade watched the Scholar.

name: Darkness Enthroned
flavourText: Hold in your hand the darkness and never will the light blind you.

name: Forbidden Flame
flavourText: The minds of those studied utterly by the Cleansing Fire continue to think and dream and beg for silence...

name: Bated Breath
flavourText: At knifepoint, a moment's hesitation means death.

name: Fluid Motion
flavourText: Even the strongest of steel can be made to bend.

name: Auxium
flavourText: As long as the soul is unfettered, so is the body.

name: Lioneye's Fall
flavourText: The shield crab does not leave his shell unless it is forced to, and even then, it knows to keep its distance.

name: Natural Affinity
flavourText: You can take the girl out of the woods, but you can't take the woods out of the girl.

name: Reckless Defence
flavourText: There's no motivation for genius quite like desperation.

name: Tempered Mind
flavourText: Any thought, no matter how fleeting, changes the thinker.

name: Tempered Flesh
flavourText: We are born raw and untested, and we are shaped by life.

name: String of Servitude
flavourText: For the Vaal, the relationship between slave and master was as intimate and volatile as that of lovers.

name: Mother's Embrace
flavourText: Drink, my children, and be strengthened.

name: Sunblast
flavourText: The sun's fury, trapped in pillars of blazing light, Explodes from its cage.

name: Stormshroud
flavourText: The true secret of the elements is that all are one and the same.

name: Powerlessness
flavourText: Your desires will mislead you.

name: Self-Flagellation
flavourText: Beg for forgiveness.

name: Realmshaper
flavourText: God's creations always begin and end with flames and ice. We should count ourselves lucky when we see neither.' - Archbishop Geofri

name: Atziri's Reflection
flavourText: At last, my beauty is beyond reproach.' - Atziri, Queen of the Vaal

name: Atziri's Promise
flavourText: Death needs not your understanding. It needs only your loyalty.' - Atziri, Queen of the Vaal

name: Kaom's Primacy
flavourText: One by one, Kaom slaughtered the weakest tribe leaders until the others leapt to join his cause.

name: Vaults of Atziri
flavourText: Should I depart this mortal coil, so shall all of my treasures.' - Atziri, Queen of the Vaal

name: Atziri's Disfavour
flavourText: I do not believe in disguising my disappointment.' - Atziri, Queen of the Vaal

name: Atziri's Rule
flavourText: Bow before her... or suffer the most gruelling death imaginable.

name: Clayshaper
flavourText: There is nothing, flesh, spirit, or stone Free from our hunger for dominion.

name: Thousand Ribbons
flavourText: Night of a Thousand Ribbons (lore)|The night of a thousand ribbons To remember the day of a thousand flames When Sarn burned And was born again

name: Victario's Influence
flavourText: Every life is a story. If you're not writing your own, you'd better know who's writing it for you!' - Victario, the People's Poet

name: Rigwald's Hunt
flavourText: The Greatwolf is with us! Gaius Sentari flees! Let us give chase, for today, my brothers and sisters, we are finally free!

name: Cloak of Defiance
flavourText: When the throat roars, As eyes weep, When the hand grips hard With trembling fingers, When belly twists Yet legs stand strong, That is the work Of the Defiant Heart.

name: Daresso's Defiance
flavourText: When your back is against the wall, And your opponent is bleeding you dry, There is only one appropriate response: Unbridled, overwhelming violence.' - Daresso, the Sword King

name: Saqawal's Nest
flavourText: The First of the Sky was the Last of the First. It was he who showed us that our limits are self-imposed, that what we take for law may just be an illusion.

name: Montoya
flavourText: They cried "Montoya, por favor" as he tore across the shore.

name: AlkLFG
flavourText: He saw the exile fall, raised his arms, and chat roared "alkLFG".

name: NoBitches Herald
flavourText: He who cannot triumph in action seeks victory in argument.

name: Yami
flavourText: High Priest of the Church of the Dose, his decree and cleave are absolute.

name: Ursarion
flavourText: Revered by all Doseurs, the Archbishop Ursarion rules the Temple of the Dose.
